            <title>[PIG-955] Skewed join generates  incorrect results </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-955</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SkewedPartitioner doesn&apos;t partition the skewed keys in partition table (first table) correctly. This can cause data loss.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
